{"tid":727777,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Scarlett Johansson 新片飾演邪骨大亨","createTime":"2018-07-03T09:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T09:42:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfbd0903de6d2f4285f11538dde918191bc8144","tid":727777,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"斯嘉麗&middot;約翰遜將出演一個厲害、複雜的角色，她將與魯伯特&middot;桑德斯(《攻殼機動隊》)再合作，主演桑德斯導演新片《Rub &amp; Tug》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《Rub &amp; Tug》是基於真人真事改編的電影。斯嘉麗在其中飾演Jean Marie Gill，一個1970年代在匹茲堡從事非法按摩和色情業的犯罪大佬，也掌握助鋼人隊在NFL建立王朝的合成代謝類固醇產業鏈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她有深愛的女友Cynthia，也參與變裝，標誌性形象是一個壯實的男裝女子，並與同志社群交好以擴大自己的帝國。最終她的物理身份變為了男性，以Dante &quot;Tex&quot; Gill之名為人所知，被媒體描述為&ldquo;模糊的男人，模糊的女人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n故事的情感核心就將是Gill和Cynthia熾烈的愛情，這從某個角度定義了Gill是怎樣的人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2018/07/scarlett-johansson-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-crime-queen-rub-and-tug-new-regency-rupert-sandersn-tale-of-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-king-1202419182/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2018%2F07%2Fscarlett-johansson-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-crime-queen-rub-and-tug-new-regency-rupert-sandersn-tale-of-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-king-1202419182%2F&d=Hbpg4j%2F5NhQYtgRbQA9tJMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=4f962f64\" target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2018/07/scarlett-johansson-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-crime-queen-rub-and-tug-new-regency-rupert-sandersn-tale-of-pittsburgh-massage-parlor-king-1202419182/</a>"},{"pid":"93d0db65d1c09818c5a11f8d1a60b94b63f9c082","tid":727777,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"真係好勁"},{"pid":"cbf912796511d1404b2ff46f18d6a218f645f67c","tid":727777,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T09:42:57.000Z","msg":"等睇ML<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}